I'm dead.

17
00:03:29,409 --> 00:03:32,071
- Well, that should simplify matters for somebody.
- Who?

18
00:03:32,145 --> 00:03:35,979
Hillerman. He says he's gonna kill you
for up to six months' back rent.

19
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:49,353
- You remind me of my father.
- Is that a proposition?

20
00:03:49,429 --> 00:03:51,363
Come on.

21
00:03:51,431 --> 00:03:54,559
You both love to read
the obituaries.

22
